{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/scene_bg.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"},{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/scene_01.png","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/scene_01.png","visible":"hide"}]},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/scene_03.png","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaFront"}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_23014.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day03.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime04","chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-1"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So, we were able to prevent her from@contracting until Walpurgisnacht.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-2"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But Madoka can't stand to watch@the city getting destroyed..."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-3"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...and she ultimately ends up@making a contract with Kyubey."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-4"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So, we need to defeat Walpurgisnacht@on our own."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-5"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That's correct."},{"chara":[{"id":200200,"motion":0},{"id":200902,"motion":0}],"nameNarration":"","narration":"[surround:8060_openpaper]*Rustle*","narrationEffect":"in","textAvClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-6"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I've written down every detail we've@discovered about this month on the flowchart."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-7"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]The sections where Kyubey attempted@to get in contact with Madoka have@been marked in red."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-8"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]It's possible we may not need to watch over@her at all times for the unmarked sections."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-9"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But we can't be sure about that...right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-10"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]If the triggering conditions remain unchanged,@events should flow exactly as before..."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-11"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But if our actions diverge even by a little,@the flowchart could be altered."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-12"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Regardless of whether those actions@involve Madoka directly."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-13"},{"id":200201,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Like a cascade of dominos, the smallest@action can cause unintended results...@A butterfly effect."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-14"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But, if we don't take the risk@of diverging from the flowchart..."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-15"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]...we may not be able to beat@Walpurgisnacht."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-16"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]There are two ways to go about this."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-17"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]The first is to collect as many Grief Seeds@as possible."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-18"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]If we can use our magic without holding back,@we'll have more firepower at our disposal."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-19"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]We'll have to collect the maximum number@of Grief Seeds available, while depleting@as little magic as possible."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-20"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]We've already noted down information@on each Witch's location, time of@appearance, and strategies to beat it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-21"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Yeah. If the enemy follows the same patterns,@we won't need to use my foresight."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-22"},{"id":200902,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But that alone won't be enough."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200201,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-23"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]The key component of our plan@to defeat Walpurgisnacht..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-24"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...is you, Mabayu."},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200902,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-25"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Hwuh?@...M-me?!"},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910103-050-25"}]},"version":3}
